{"id":"ea42bc88-f504-4eed-8a6b-63ee896ae93d","title":"1547/12/17: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"c5fbe1a6-14f4-4ae4-8d03-c4d13705ef37","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [December 17th, 1547].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d91f73ef-583e-49b3-947e-0ced70a965c1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3309251a-0de6-422f-9c15-ecd6fc6d4fd2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c8411b12-74f0-4880-8262-931d8efff7b9","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":30,"value":"440fd1e7-2346-4bc5-b84d-2a9954c90602","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8a461a7a-f81c-4d4f-a3d9-219e0c8be30c","type":"style/superscript","start":23,"end":24,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"1a368b35-b892-4913-84ac-b5993c02dc61","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"62c8ae7f-f784-4b24-b1d9-d02c5bfff8b4","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"28663cac-706c-408c-9447-61d6e3fa9145","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"cc78202f-7a41-4fac-8b37-f473c1a7191f","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d57e901e-d7a1-4718-a496-c0f29c73dc13","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ec6aacd7-e29f-4c36-b819-efb423fdc09f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"0ad8bfe5-f5b9-41e1-911d-89209b312d37","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"bd36f155-9605-4cd8-9671-11288c01a9fe","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I learn from thy letter that a lawsuit is pending with reference to certain lands at Settignano and that thou desirest me to send a power of attorney so that ye may defend the action. The power of attorney will be sent with this letter, and I\u00A0think I ought at the same time to send you a book of\u00A0contracts which I caused to be copied out in proper form by Ser Giovanni da Romena, and for which I had to pay 18 ducats. The contract for the said land cannot fail to be among them: and when I send the book I will at the same time send a number of contracts and ratifications and other papers which\u00A0are worth all I possess in the world. I would like thee, therefore, to seek out some trustworthy carrier and tell him to come and see me when he is in Rome, when I will give him the bundle containing the said\u00A0documents. It will weigh about 20 pounds (libbre). Thou art to settle the price with him, and do not quarrel over an odd half-crown if he deliver the parcel to thee safely. Tell him, moreover, that when he brings me thy letter acknowledging its arrival I will also give him something for his trouble. About the shop; Guicciardino writes to me saying thou hast begged of him to go into partnership with him, and thou sayest that he has begged it of thee. It does not matter either way so long as ye arrive at a clear understanding, for we have none too many friends or relations that we can afford to quarrel among ourselves. As to our family name, I should certainly add \u0022Simone\u0022 to it, and if it be thought over-long by those who do not care to read it all through they\u00A0can leave it alone.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"1f4bf423-85a0-4c95-9eb3-fd5c3b2c0d54","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4b465a0d-bafa-4c81-8f55-108580c